                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">17.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Of the funds appropriated in this item, $10,000,000 shall be allocated on a one-time basis for the Children’s Holistic Immigration
