                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">18.</td>
                        <td colspan="5" valign="top" width="288">Of the funds appropriated in this item, $14,500,000 shall be allocated on a one-time basis for the Holocaust Survivors Assistance
                           Program to continue to provide services through the 2025–26 fiscal year and shall be available for encumbrance or expenditure
                           until June 30, 2027.
