                           <div style="">Of the funds appropriated in this item, $12,000,000 shall be available to support foster youth programs pursuant to Section
                              89348 of the Education Code.
                           </div>
                        </td>
                        <td valign="bottom" width="80"></td>
                     </tr>
                     <tr>
                        <td valign="top" width="24"></td>
                        <td valign="top" width="24">2.1.</td>
